c: 9
v: 59
t: "wlw 'ana hwla' aladhin yeybwnk fi qismat alsadaqat raduu bima qism allah warasulah lhm, wqalu: hasbuna allh, sayutina allah min fdlh, wyetyna rasulih mimaa atah allh, 'iinaa narghab 'ana ywse allah elyna, fyghnyna ean alsdqt waean sadaqat alnaas. law faealuu dhlk lakan khyrana lahum wajda"